# Source inputs for the hash-pinned clone-layer lock (requirements-clone.lock).
# Regenerate with `make lock-clone` (runs in a linux py3.11 container — torch
# is platform-specific so this lock is NOT cross-platform; it targets the
# linux clone Docker image). chatterbox-tts is installed --no-deps separately.
#
# The base runtime is a constraint so shared deps stay pinned to requirements.lock.
-c requirements.lock
--extra-index-url https://download.pytorch.org/whl/cpu
torch==2.6.0+cpu
torchaudio==2.6.0+cpu
-r requirements-clone.txt
